This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to identify implicit beliefs and intentions in user-generated text. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses LSTM networks, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) research. Additionally, the paper deals with classification algorithms (cs.IR) and utilizes annotated datasets (cs.SI).
